{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I made myself two years older, being 1928.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And surprisingly enough, we managed to stay together, which was most unusual.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Because the camp organizations were instructed to split brothers and fathers and children to break them apart.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "The events then after we were taken to the lower part of the camp, which was called [INAUDIBLE], which is the tent camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Because there was a middle lager and a [? grosslager. ?] Buchenwald was a very large camp, was to very large extent by inmates of German political [INAUDIBLE]-- it means inmate-- Norwegians, French, Dutch, and Russian prisoners of war later, not at that time, Practically of all nationalities.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Jews-- you Know, everybody had a triangle of a color.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, yellow was for Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was very bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you had a black, you were a gypsy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you had a green, you were a criminal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you had a mauve triangle, you were homosexual.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you were a political prisoner, like the communists and socialists, it was a red triangle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, the, worst of it was if somebody had like a Magen David, which was a yellow triangle being a Jew and a cross with a red one, that he's a communist or socialist, a political plus a Jew.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the bottom of the line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, I'm just trying to explain to you the certain marks which had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from then on, you were not known by name, but by a number.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mine was 66,630-- 66,226.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father's was 25.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my brother's was 27.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They tried to sandwich me in the middle of it, so if, if we ever get split, either I go with my father or I go with my brother.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, because I was literally at a very young age.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
